# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
# AI-Powered Smart Service Marketplace
# Backend Environment Variables
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values
# ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━

# ── Server ─────────────────────────────────
PORT=5000
NODE_ENV=development

# ── MongoDB ────────────────────────────────
# Get from: https://cloud.mongodb.com
# Format: mongodb+srv://<username>:<password>@cluster0.xxxxx.mongodb.net/smart-marketplace?retryWrites=true&w=majority
MONGODB_URI=your_mongodb_uri_here

# ── JWT Authentication ──────────────────────
# Generate with: node -e "console.log(require('crypto').randomBytes(64).toString('hex'))"
JWT_SECRET=your_super_secret_jwt_key_here_min_32_chars
JWT_EXPIRES_IN=7d

# ── Google Gemini API ───────────────────────
# Get from: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key_here

# ── Google Maps ────────────────────────────
# Get from: https://console.cloud.google.com
# Enable: Maps JavaScript API, Geocoding API, Places API, Distance Matrix API
GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY=your_google_maps_api_key_here

# ── Cloudinary (File Uploads) ───────────────
# Get from: https://cloudinary.com/console
CLOUDINARY_CLOUD_NAME=your_cloudinary_cloud_name
CLOUDINARY_API_KEY=your_cloudinary_api_key
CLOUDINARY_API_SECRET=your_cloudinary_api_secret

# ── Razorpay (Payments) ─────────────────────
# Get from: https://dashboard.razorpay.com/app/keys
RAZORPAY_KEY_ID=your_razorpay_key_id
RAZORPAY_KEY_SECRET=your_razorpay_key_secret

# ── Email (SMTP via Gmail) ──────────────────
# Use Gmail App Password (not your regular password)
# Guide: https://myaccount.google.com/apppasswords
SMTP_HOST=smtp.gmail.com
SMTP_PORT=587
SMTP_USER=your_email@gmail.com
SMTP_PASS=your_gmail_app_password

# ── App URLs ────────────────────────────────
FRONTEND_URL=http://localhost:3000
ADMIN_EMAIL=admin@marketplace.com

# ── Rate Limiting ───────────────────────────
RATE_LIMIT_WINDOW_MS=900000
RATE_LIMIT_MAX=100
